high_descs: Go left and then left again to face the round table.
Pick the black mug up from the table.
Go left and then right to face the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge, shut the door and then open the door and pick up the mug.
Go right and turn to face the round table.
Put the mug under the coffee maker on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug under a coffee maker.

high_descs: turn left and head towards the door, then turn left to face the table.
pick up the coffee cup from the coffee machine
Turn towards the left and head towards the fridge.
open the fridge door and place the coffee cup in front of the egg, close the door and wait a few seconds, open the door and pick up the coffee cup and close the door.
Return to the kitchen table with the coffee maker.
Place the coffee cup on to the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Chill the coffee cup in the fridge and return it to the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the round wooden table.
Pick up the coffee mug that is in the coffee machine on the round table.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and begin walking across the room, hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge doors and put the mug on the top shelf, then close the doors, after a couple seconds open the fridge and remove the mug, then close the doors again.
Turn right and walk over to the round wooden table, then turn right and begin walking across the room, hang a left and walk over to the door then turn left and walk up to the round wooden table.
Place the chilled coffee mug into the coffee machine on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled coffee mug in the coffee machine.
